(Luis Nogales wey be 45 years don dey elected to board dis Brewer).

Mr. Nogales wey be former Presido of United Press International and Univision Spanish-language network, most recently co-founded Nogales Castro Partners, one media company wey be California based media acquisition firm.

Mr. Nogales wey be di first Hispanic person to serve as Coors director, na im join di board na im add am to nine.

